author: 박차고
title: Fast and good. We will give you a refund within 14 days.
review:
I was using a different virtual drive, but I tried it on a 14-day trial and it's faster and more comfortable. However, instead of using Windows frequently, I tried to quit the free trial within the evaluation period, but it was difficult to find a way. Answering many similar questions didn't help either. Share how you found it.
App store -> Click your ID at the bottom left -> View information in the top row -> Click'Manage' on the right side of'Subscription' at the bottom of the third'Management' tab from the top -> Find the app you want to unsubscribe and'Subscribe cancel'
You can do it in order. For reference, if you are using the same App Store ID, you can also unsubscribe from your iPhone or iPad.
I hope it was helpful for those who were embarrassed because I couldn't cancel my free trial like me.
original_title: 빠르고 좋습니다. 14일 이내 환불이 가능해서 방법 적어봅니다.
original_review:
다른 버츄어 드라이브 쓰고 있었는데 14일 평가판 써보니 더 빠르고 편하고 좋습니다. 다만 윈도우를 자주쓰는 편이 아니라 평가 기한 이내에 무료체험을 그만두려 했는데 방법을 찾기가 어렵더라고요. 비슷한 많은 질문에 대한 답변도 도움이 되지 않았고요. 찾은 방법을 공유합니다.
App store -> 맨 왼쪽 아래의 자기 아이디 클릭 -> 맨 윗줄의 정보 보기 -> 위에서 세 번째 '관리'탭 아래쪽에 '구독' 오른쪽에 있는 '관리' 클릭 -> 구독을 취소하고 싶은 어플 찾아서 '구독취소'
순서로 하시면 됩니다. 참고로 같은 앱스토어 아이디를 쓰고 계시면 아이폰이나 아이패드에서도 구독취소가 가능합니다.
저처럼 무료체험 하려다가 취소가 안돼서 당황하셨을 분들에게 도움이 되었기 바랍니다.

author: Sabinius
title: EXCELLENT VIRTUAL MACHINE
review:
Virtual Machine with excellent software support, worth the price. It is also the only one that can be installed from the Mac App Store, and this is an unimaginable advantage in terms of security.
I try not to install any app that is not a drag and drop executable in the applications folder, because once the password is set, that app can do anything it wants. Mac App Store is the only way to be truly sure of what you install.
Automatic and functional installation of some distros and windows without interaction.
10 and praise
original_review:
Virtual Machine con ottimo support per il software, vale il prezzo. Inoltre è l'unica installabile da Mac App Store, e questo è un vantaggio inimmaginabile in termini di sicurezza.
Cerco di non installare nessuna app che non sia un eseguibile drag and drop nella cartella applicazioni, in quanto, una volta messa la password, quell'app può fare tutto quello che vuole. Mac App Store è l'unico modo per essere realmente sicuri di ciò che si installa.
Installazione di alcune distro e di windows automatica e funzionante senza interazione.
10 e lode

author: mtnscll
title: For $80/year they'll track you and force ads at you
review:
Been paying these people for 3 years and finally had enough and moving to VMware Fusion, which is much better.  Straw that broke my back was Parallels insistence on showing me ads for their other products every week. I tried opting-out, tried opening support cases, these pople just don't care.
If you're trying to play a game this *MIGHT* work for you.  If you need to run VM's or do anything business-related or "mission-critical" stay far away.

title: Exaggerated price
review: Price far too high, despite the excellent service. original_review: Prezzo decisamente troppo alto, nonostante l'ottimo servizio. E poco apprezzabile il modo in cui viene valutato il giudizio medio: le recensioni con una stella sono ben superiori rispetto a quelle a cinque stelle... La media matematica dei giudizi dà 2,7, non 4,4. Se interessasse davvero la soddisfazione dei clienti, oltre che al profitto, ci sarebbe da rivedere alcune cose.

author: Michael3831
title: No test possible without a direct subscription purchase. What to do?
review:
I already have Parallels Desktop for Mac running in an older version. I then read about this lite version.
Since I'm only dealing with a macOS VM, I find this interesting. Only 4 Mac programs are required, which are not supported in the current version 10.15. So I downloaded the app and wanted to test it. When I open it for the first time, however, I am asked directly to complete the annual subscription. I cannot use any function before.
And it should only cost something for the Windows version (to my knowledge) and otherwise be free of charge. I'm only interested in macOS virtualization.
@Paralles support:
The concept is so daunting. It's a shame. Even if the mac OS virtualization should also cost, I would like to be able to test it at least for now.
I look forward to your feedback and solutions. Thank you.
original_title: Kein Test ohne direkten Abo-Kauf möglich. Was tun?
original_review:
Ich habe bereits Parallels Desktop für Mac in einer älteren Version in Betrieb. Habe dann von dieser Lite Version gelesen.
Da es bei mir nur um ein macOS VM geht, finde ich das interessent. Es werden lediglich 4 Mac Programme benötigt, die in der aktuellen Version 10.15 nicht unterstützt werden. Daher habe ich die App runtergeladen und wollte es testen. Beim ersten Öffnen werde ich aber direkt aufgefordert, das Jahresabo abzuschließen. Vorher kann ich keine Funktion nutzen. 
Und dabei soll es ja nur für die Windows-Version (meines Wissens) etwas kosten und sonst kostenfrei sein. Mir geht es ja nur um eine macOS Virtualisierung. 
@Paralles support:
Das Konzept schreckt so sehr ab. Sehr schade. Selbst wenn die mac OS Virtualisierung auch kosten sollte, so möchte ich doch zumindest erstmal testen können.
Freu mich gerne über Feedback und Lösungen. Danke.
